{{Otheruses|Orion}}
'''''Orion''''' was a [[Lambda-class T-4a shuttle/Legends|Lambda-class T-4a shuttle]] that carried [[Sabacc/Legends|Sabacc]] players from the ''[[Dunari's Rest]]'' when the latter was attacked by Imperial forces. It made it to the hyperspace intact thanks to assistance from the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]].

